tv.matchstick.flint

Interface Flint.ApplicationConnectionResult

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Result
    Enclosing class:
    Flint

    public static interface Flint.ApplicationConnectionResult
extends Result
    Interface to display current application connection status.
    When a Flint application connected to a remote receiver, this object will be returned. And it contains this Flint application's meta data and current status.
    See Also:
